            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As I myself am from the Education Department,I know what efforts a teacher goes through.I would really appreciate you for all the hard work you have done.I did not expect at all that this level of hard work would be done in the nursery class. Or will the child's learning remain so strong.\nOr all this has become possible because of your efforts. I have seen my daughter's excitement every day to go to school. just because she knew Priyanka ma'am would be there.It is best that you provide additional efforts according to the student's requirements. And your coordination with parents is commendable.🫡👏👏👏✨",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
