          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-29",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had a wonderful experience at Manav Rachna International School, Sector-14. The school is blessed to have teachers who develop a bond not only with kids but also with their parents. Kids are also provided with amazing opportunities for holistic development. There is a focus on not only academics but also on extracurriculars. Really appreciate the great efforts being put in by the MRIS management. In coming time, this school is going to achieve next level heights under able guidance of Mrs. Wadhwa and Mrs. Kathuria.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
