          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-24",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The best part in Manav Rachna (Sector-14) is that the teachers let the student question status quo and work very hard with the student to strengthen any weak area. We have personal  experience of this and are grateful to all the teachers of Class XI B as they never gave up on my Son and kept on encouraging him to do better. The infrastructure of School is absolutely World Class and is probably one of the best in the Country today and certainly is the best in Delhi-NCR.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
