            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "School plays an important role in developing the overall growth of children and MRIS is playing commendable role in it.  The opportunities for extracurricular activities are fantastic. Thank you for your hard work in supporting my daughter Parnika Devacharya .Your patience and commitment to supporting my child has mean a lot to our family.\nWith your guidance, our daughter has developed into a confident and capable child. Thank you for being such an important part in our child’s development.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
