          "datePublished": "2024-02-22",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "What an Amazing School !!! Teachers, Curriculum, Student Support, Infrastructure everything is Top Notch...  A wonderful learning experience created for the students by the faculty. Here, Students learn not for the sake of learning but for the fun of it. Thank You MRIS - 14.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Manav Rachna International School - Sector 14"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Manish Sekhri"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-22",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent of Bhavvya Sekhri of grade IX-C, my experience with the school has been exceptionally positive. From academics, sports, art, technology to events and webinars, the school focuses on all rounded and holistic development of our children. I've been with the school for the past 10 years, and I feel very connected and valued being a member of this community. The teachers are very passionate and dedicated, ensuring that each child receives individual attention and support at all times. Children also get the opportunity to participate in all extracurricular activities which enrich them with important life and social skills like teamwork, leadership and time management. They also assist the child to participate in events, webinars and competitions which will help them to develop confidence and learn from their failures.\nI am grateful to be a part of it and am confident that my child is receiving an education that will prepare them for success in the future.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
